5
00:00:12,770 --> 00:00:16,840
In 2014, China launched a war against pollution.

6
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:18,200
But it’s been tough.

7
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:19,200
Turns out,

8
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:22,870
it’s much easier to arrest dissidents than
smog.

9
00:00:22,870 --> 00:00:24,060
Which is why Beijing police

10
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,000
are now being armed with vacuum cleaners.

11
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,560
Not for the smog.

12
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:30,680
It’s to knock out the dissidents.

13
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:32,450
