14
00:00:32,450 --> 00:00:34,160
But in terms of pollution,

15
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:36,040
China has been pushing ahead.

16
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:37,500
The Chinese Communist Party has said

17
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,510
it wants to be a world leader

18
00:00:39,510 --> 00:00:42,000
in transitioning out of “dirty energy”

19
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:43,780
and “going green”!

20
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:44,850
For example,

21
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:47,630
as Northern China enters a freezing winter,

22
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:49,610
the Ministry of Environmental Protection

23
00:00:49,610 --> 00:00:52,820
issued a vaguely worded notice to 28 cities

24
00:00:52,820 --> 00:00:55,489
to keep air pollution under control

25
00:00:55,489 --> 00:00:56,870
by speeding up the transition

26
00:00:56,870 --> 00:00:59,980
from coal to natural gas.

27
00:00:59,980 --> 00:01:02,289
Local officials began arresting people

28
