34
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:17,390
Wait, what’s that Shelley?

35
00:01:17,390 --> 00:01:20,150
They don’t have Christmas stockings in China?

36
00:01:20,150 --> 00:01:22,500
Ok, well never mind then.

37
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:25,580
Arresting people is obviously the next logical
step.

38
00:01:25,580 --> 00:01:27,960
But anyway, it sounds good—

39
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:30,580
stop people from burning that dirty coal.

40
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:31,580
After all,

41
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:34,070
we’re talking about pollution that’s so
bad,

42
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:36,060
a University of Chicago study found

43
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:39,000
it takes three years off the average person’s
life

44
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,290
in Northern China.

45
00:01:41,290 --> 00:01:42,350
And in exchange,

46
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:44,780
Chinese authorities promised they would transition

47
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:47,380
everyone to natural gas.

48
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:49,740
Just one small problem:

49
00:01:49,740 --> 00:01:51,180
In a lot of areas,

50
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:54,980
