110
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:10,489
Let’s just hope it doesn’t also backfire

111
00:04:10,489 --> 00:04:12,540
for Apple CEO Tim cook.

112
00:04:12,540 --> 00:04:14,260
While he was in China this month,

113
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:17,509
he said, “China’s environmental leadership
is very clear,

114
00:04:17,509 --> 00:04:20,299
and it aligns completely with Apple’s values,”

115
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:23,760
Sounds like Apple’s values might be a tad
rotten.

116
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:25,780
Oh, and another thing.

117
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:27,980
Most of China’s coal pollution doesn’t
even

118
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:30,470
come from individuals burning coal in their
homes

119
00:04:30,470 --> 00:04:32,040
to keep warm.

120
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:35,210
It mostly comes from power plants and factories.

121
00:04:35,210 --> 00:04:38,419
And it just so happens that more than 70%
of factories

122
00:04:38,419 --> 00:04:42,070
don’t meet China’s air pollution standards.

123
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:45,009
But instead of installing better pollution
controls,

124
00:04:45,009 --> 00:04:47,169
factories have also been told to reduce

125
00:04:47,169 --> 00:04:49,259
or stop burning coal.

126
00:04:49,259 --> 00:04:50,990
So that also means a lot of factories

127
00:04:50,990 --> 00:04:54,259
