135
00:05:10,100 --> 00:05:12,220
I see what you did there.

136
00:05:12,229 --> 00:05:14,319
How could there be such a big screw up?

137
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:16,449
Well, in addition to the inefficiency

138
00:05:16,449 --> 00:05:18,250
of top-down directives,

139
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,210
part of the reasons is that estimates

140
00:05:20,210 --> 00:05:22,650
for how much natural gas was needed

141
00:05:22,650 --> 00:05:24,189
